OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FWords by Sarah Lock
OL,7,FThe US military reportedly used
OL,8,FAnthropic's Claude when it launched
OL,9,Fits first attack on Iran almost one
OL,10,Fweek ago, shining a spotlight on the
OL,11,Fuse of large-language artificial
OL,12,Fintelligence models in modern warfare.
OL,14,FThe new era of artificial intelligence
OL,15,Fpermits military decisions to be made
OL,16,Ffar more quickly, providing an edge to
OL,17,Fthose utilising it in war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FBut what are its capabilities, and
OL,6,Fwhat are the risks of automating
OL,7,Fwarfare that has real human
OL,8,Fconsequences? ITV News explains
OL,10,FArtificial intelligence is becoming
OL,11,Fmore sophisticated
OL,13,FArtificial Intelligence (AI) has been
OL,14,Fused in the military for decades.
OL,15,FDuring the Cold War, the US Navy used
OL,16,Fforms of AI to process vast amounts of
OL,17,Fsurveillance data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FBy the 1990's, they were using AI to
OL,6,Fschedule the transportation of
OL,7,Fsupplies or personnel, saving millions
OL,8,Fof dollars in the process.
OL,10,FBut over the years, AI has become
OL,11,Fincreasingly more sophisticated, with
OL,12,FIsrael reportedly using it in Gaza as
OL,13,Fto select potential buildings and
OL,14,Fpeople to strike, according to
OL,15,Fintelligence sources.
OL,17,FIt has also become incredibly useful
OL,18,Fin military defence because of its
OL,19,Fability to identify missiles and
OL,20,Fforming a response in a very quick
OL,21,Famount of time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FLast year, Ukraine deployed a fully AI-
OL,6,Fcontrolled turret, designed to detect
OL,7,Fand shoot down Russian drones without
OL,8,Fany human involvement.
OL,10,FHow has the US been using AI before
OL,11,Fthe Iran war?
OL,13,FThe US Department of Defence struck
OL,14,Fdeals with several major AI firms in
OL,15,FJuly last year, but Anthropic, which
OL,16,Fcreates a system called Claude, was
OL,17,Fthe only model permitted to be
OL,18,Fdeployed on the military's classified
OL,19,Fsystems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FThe company said it had been
OL,6,F"extensively deployed" across the
OL,7,Fdepartment and national security
OL,8,Fagencies, for "intelligence analysis,
OL,9,Fmodelling and simulation, operational
OL,10,Fplanning, cyber operations, and more".
OL,12,FClaude was reportedly also used in the
OL,13,Fmilitary operation in Venezuela, which
OL,14,Fsaw US forces capture and extract
OL,15,FPresident Nicolas Maduro from the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,26,@wD@Prp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,FOperational details of how it was
OL,6,Fprecisely used aren't available, but
OL,7,FDavid Galbreath, Professor of War and
OL,8,FTechnology at the University of Bath,
OL,9,Ftold ITV News it was likely used for
OL,10,Fintelligence.
OL,12,F"You would have had lots of drones and
OL,13,Fother types of aircraft hoovering up
OL,14,Fdata. How people are moving throughout
OL,15,Fthe city, all the telecoms that are
OL,16,Fhappening, and what traffic is like,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772917555
OL,3,CHow is AI shaping the conflict in Iran?
OL,5,F"You're accumulating a large amount of
OL,6,Fdata. And that's where those large
OL,7,Flanguage models are particularly
OL,8,Fuseful in being able to collect all
OL,9,Fthat data and then trying to then show
OL,10,Fintelligence officers some of the key
OL,11,Fpatterns that emerge out of that."
OL,13,FThe intelligence officers would then
OL,14,Fuse human judgment to decipher how
OL,15,Fthose patterns could be useful for
OL,16,Foperations.
OL,18,FThe Trump administration and Claude's
OL,19,Frelationship breakdown
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
